juniDhcpv6LocalServerBindingsInfinite.name: juniDhcpv6LocalServerBindingsInfinite
juniDhcpv6LocalServerBindingsInfinite.description: If true, then this binding will be maintained indefinitely. If false, then this binding will expire in accordance with the value of juniDhcpv6LocalServerBindingsExpireTime.

juniDhcpv6LocalServerBindingsExpireTime.name: juniDhcpv6LocalServerBindingsExpireTime
juniDhcpv6LocalServerBindingsExpireTime.description: If juniDhcpv6LocalServerBindingsInfinite is false, then this is the time remaining prior to expiration of the address binding associated with this entry.
